description: LeoVegas AB engages in the mobile gaming business. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm and currently employs 817 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2016-03-17. The firm operates as a provider of online games available on mobile devices, tablets and computers. The firm specializes in online casino entertainment and offers a wide range of games, such as roulette, slots, live games, jackpots, table games, blackjack and baccarat, among others. The firm's games are built using graphics and sounds, as well as allow to play with familiar characters like Lara Croft, Superman and many more. The firm offers a variety of virtual experiencies, such as Monte Carlo casinos, Baden-Baden casinos and Las Vegas casinos, among others. The firm has its operations domestically and in Malta.
